Purpose:
Merge the latest foundational service Terraform modules into the Production PMR using Bitbucket. This will enable foundational modules for Terraform to work effectively in production.

Scope:
The epic involves enabling and deploying the following Terraform modules as separate stories:

ECPIC-1589: Add better descriptions to disk-encryption module outputs.
ECPIC-1796: Terraform Module Testing in QUA/UAT Env - VM Disk.
ECPIC-1629: Add VM-disk attachment to VM in App L3 Landing Zone.
ECPIC-1636: Add data classification tag on Terraform ignore changes.
ECPIC-1872: Validate VM & VMSS after ignoring the changes to Custom Data.
ECPIC-1982: Re-validate Unit Testing of TFE - keyvault, storage, and Terraform test.
ECPIC-1800: Add optional parameters to load-balancer rule and probe.
ECPIC-2124: Terraform Module Testing in QUA/UAT Env - Linux VM.
ECPIC-2125: Terraform Module Testing in QUA/UAT Env - OS Image.
ECPIC-2126: Terraform Module Testing in QUA/UAT Env - Storage Container.
ECPIC-2127: Terraform Module Testing in QUA/UAT Env - Storage Table.
ECPIC-2128: Terraform Module Testing in QUA/UAT Env - Storage Queue.
ECPIC-2129: Terraform Module Testing in QUA/UAT Env - Express Route Gateway.
ECPIC-2130: Update OS-image module to publish module in CORP2 using XLR.
ECPIC-2136: Update keyvault-key module to publish module in CORP2 using XLR.
ECPIC-2135: Update storage-container module to publish module in CORP2 using XLR.
ECPIC-2137: Update storage-table module to publish module in CORP2 using XLR.
ECPIC-2138: Update storage-queue module to publish module in CORP2 using XLR.
ECPIC-2170: Terraform Module Testing in QUA/UAT Env - Keyvault Key.
ECPIC-2171: Terraform Module Testing in QUA/UAT Env - Keyvault Premium.
ECPIC-2190: CORP2 UAT release pre-work and support planned for 27th Sept 24.
ECPIC-2266: EAP CORP2 Promotion Release (04/12) - Naming Convention Terraform Module Testing.
ECPIC-2273: EAP CORP2 Promotion Release (04/12) - Storage Account Terraform Module Testing.
ECPIC-2325: Update naming convention module for azurem_monitor_metric_alert.
ECPIC-2326: Update storage account module to add timeout block.
ECPIC-2336: Testing Storage Account modules - CORP3/DEV.
